➜日本透明公厕火了，这些「全球最美公厕」你上过几个？
https://www.ifanr.com/1361332?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	11475
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361841" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu1.jpg" alt="" width="1868" height="1244" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu1.jpg 1868w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu1-768x511.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu1-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1868px) 100vw, 1868px" /></p>
<p>提起公共厕所，你的第一印象是什么？</p>
<p>这样的？</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361838" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7f1802a01fe94bd38cf47d34bc5f90af.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="1148" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7f1802a01fe94bd38cf47d34bc5f90af.jpeg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7f1802a01fe94bd38cf47d34bc5f90af-360x383.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7f1802a01fe94bd38cf47d34bc5f90af-768x816.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7f1802a01fe94bd38cf47d34bc5f90af-963x1024.jpeg 963w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>这样的？</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361844 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/a-2.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/a-2.jpg 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/a-2-360x240.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p>还是这样的？</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361836 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5f48683ea9bb62287.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="398" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5f48683ea9bb62287.jpg_e680.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5f48683ea9bb62287.jpg_e680-360x239.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>随着过去几十年中国等国掀起「<a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD_(%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8)">厕所革命</a>」，公共厕所的环境已经大有改观，但很多人依然不得不忍受「脏乱差」的厕所。</p>
<p>根据世界卫生组织和联合国儿童基金会的报告，全球还有 42 亿人缺乏安全、卫生的厕所，6.73 亿人还在露天便溺。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361833" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/159869007832544_P6921546.jpg" alt="" width="1049" height="704" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/159869007832544_P6921546.jpg 1049w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/159869007832544_P6921546-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/159869007832544_P6921546-768x515.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/159869007832544_P6921546-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1049px) 100vw, 1049px" /></p>
<p>在印度电影《厕所英雄》里，很多印度家庭因为宗教和传统习俗不在家中安装厕所，都是在露天环境中如厕，无数女性因此遭遇性侵，就此掀起了一场社会变革。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361845" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-7.jpeg" alt="" width="2811" height="4016" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-7.jpeg 2811w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-7-360x514.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-7-768x1097.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-7-717x1024.jpeg 717w" sizes="(max-width: 2811px) 100vw, 2811px" /></p>
<p><strong>公厕不仅是急人之需的基础设施，还是一个国家文明程度的体现。</strong></p>
<p>最近慈善机构「日本财团」（The Nippon Foundation）就发起了 <a href="https://tokyotoilet.jp/en/">「东京厕所」「The Tokyo Toilet」计划</a>，邀请安藤忠雄等 16 位知名建筑设计大师在东京涩谷设计 17 座公厕，以改变人们对公厕的刻板印象。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361843" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/og.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="630" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/og.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/og-360x189.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/og-768x403.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/og-1024x538.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>目前已经有 5 座厕所完工了，其中东京街头的一个透明公厕，甚至成了新的网红打卡地。</p>
<h3>普利兹克奖设计大师操刀，让这些公厕变成了网红景点</h3>
<p>在介绍这些网红公厕之前，不得不先介绍一下设计师的阵容。</p>
<p>16 位设计师中，除了大名鼎鼎的安藤忠雄，还有伊东丰雄、槇文彦、坂茂等多位获得过有「建筑界奥斯卡」之称的普利兹克奖的建筑大师。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361846" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/A1543719163.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/A1543719163.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/A1543719163-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/A1543719163-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 安藤忠雄. 图片来自：Pinterest</p>
</div>
<p>此外，号称「设计魔术师」的优衣库艺术总监佐藤可士和、三宅一生第一位女性手表设计师田村奈穗 、连「侃爷」都视为偶像的潮流教父 NIGO ，也都参与到「东京厕所」项目的设计中。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361847" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/nigo-louis-vuitton-trunk-feat.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/nigo-louis-vuitton-trunk-feat.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/nigo-louis-vuitton-trunk-feat-360x216.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/nigo-louis-vuitton-trunk-feat-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/nigo-louis-vuitton-trunk-feat-1024x614.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲NIGO. 图片来自：Highsnobiety</p>
</div>
<p>这样一个设计界的全明星组合来打造的公厕，实在不能不让人期待。</p>
<p><strong>透明公厕</strong></p>
<p>这些厕所中最受瞩目的莫过于两座透明公厕，由普利兹克奖得主坂茂操刀，外墙完全由透明玻璃组成，分别位于代代木深町小公园与春之小川公园。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361848" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1435-e1597400821833-1-2000x905.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="905" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1435-e1597400821833-1-2000x905.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1435-e1597400821833-1-2000x905-360x163.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1435-e1597400821833-1-2000x905-768x348.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1435-e1597400821833-1-2000x905-1024x463.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>为什么要将厕所这种注重隐私和安全的设施设计成透明？</p>
<p>其实这恰恰就是为了保护使用者的隐私和安全。据设计师坂茂介绍，人们对于公厕的担忧主要有两点：一是厕所是否干净清洁，二是不知道里面会不会藏着什么偷窥狂。</p>
<p>透明公厕可以让使用者解除这两个顾虑，同时你也不用担心自己在如厕的时候被外面的人一览无余。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361852" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1361-1-2000x1333.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1361-1-2000x1333.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1361-1-2000x1333-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1361-1-2000x1333-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1361-1-2000x1333-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>透明公厕采用了特殊彩色的液晶玻璃，在无人使用时可以清楚看到里面的情况，一旦有人进入厕所上锁后，玻璃就会变成不透明的磨砂状态。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361850" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-43-18.2020-08-30-06_44_26.gif" alt="" width="942" height="495" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-43-18.2020-08-30-06_44_26.gif 942w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-43-18.2020-08-30-06_44_26-360x189.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-43-18.2020-08-30-06_44_26-768x404.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 942px) 100vw, 942px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 图片来自：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1GcyTKfj_wQ">YouTube</a></p>
</div>
<p>同时出于安全考量，当有人进入厕所后 30 分钟没出来玻璃会自动变回透明并解锁，以防止有人晕倒在厕所后失去意识不被发现。</p>
<p>之所以能实现这样的效果，是因为这种液晶玻璃内遍布着液晶分子，通电后液晶分子呈直线排列，光线可直接透过，玻璃变得透明。而在切断电源后，液晶分子的排列将变得不规则，光线被散射，玻璃则呈现不透明的状态</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361851" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-46-33.2020-08-30-06_47_49.gif" alt="" width="942" height="495" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-46-33.2020-08-30-06_47_49.gif 942w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-46-33.2020-08-30-06_47_49-360x189.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-06-46-33.2020-08-30-06_47_49-768x404.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 942px) 100vw, 942px" /></p>
<p>除此之外，透明公厕的玻璃到了夜晚还会亮起来，从远处看就像一个五彩斑斓的灯笼，还能作为路灯方便路人和在夜晚使用公厕的市民。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361842" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1334" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu-2.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/titu-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>这两个厕所推出以后吸引了不少人前来打卡，YouTube 上有不少博主前去拍摄了体验视频，获得了几百万的播放量。</p>
<p>可也有人表示担忧，如果电路发生故障，玻璃突然变透明，那不就相当于在上厕所的时候被突然踢开门吗？</p>
<p><strong>包容所有人的红色礼盒</strong></p>
<p>除了透明公厕，在视觉上最具冲击力的就是田村奈穂设计的红色公厕。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361853" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_07_A-2000x1318.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1318" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_07_A-2000x1318.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_07_A-2000x1318-360x237.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_07_A-2000x1318-768x506.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_07_A-2000x1318-1024x675.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>厕所位于惠比寿车站旁狭长的三角区域，尽管空间不大，但田村奈穂红色很好利用了这个地形特点。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361854 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_01-640x422.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="422" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_01-640x422.jpg 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_01-640x422-360x237.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361859" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/r.png" alt="" width="983" height="341" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/r.png 983w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/r-360x125.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/r-768x266.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 983px) 100vw, 983px" /></p>
<p>这一设计的灵感来源于日本一种传统的礼物包装方式 Origata，将公厕设计成类似包装折纸的三个空间。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361858" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_06_B-2000x1348.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1348" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_06_B-2000x1348.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_06_B-2000x1348-360x243.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_06_B-2000x1348-768x518.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_06_B-2000x1348-1024x690.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>在日本传统中，Origata 折纸包装上的皱褶表达了送礼人的心意，而田村奈穂希望这座公厕能体现涩谷对各地游客的热情款待之情。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361856" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_10-2000x1361.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1361" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_10-2000x1361.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_10-2000x1361-360x245.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_10-2000x1361-768x523.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HigashiToilet_10-2000x1361-1024x697.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>同时田村奈穂也受到了纽约一些 LGBTQ 社区的启发，希望这座公厕能满足不同群体多样化的需求，称为一个保障安全、隐私和紧急需求的公共空间。</p>
<p><strong>游乐园公厕</strong></p>
<p>而小孩子最喜欢的，一定是建筑大师槇文彦在惠比寿东公园内设计的公厕。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361863" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2190-1-2000x1333.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2190-1-2000x1333.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2190-1-2000x1333-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2190-1-2000x1333-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2190-1-2000x1333-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>由于公园内有一个章鱼造型的滑梯，被当地人戏称为「章鱼公园」，这座公园也被很多孩子当成游乐场，而槇文彦在把新的公厕称为「章鱼公园」内的「鱿鱼公厕」。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361861" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2162-1-2000x1333.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2162-1-2000x1333.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2162-1-2000x1333-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2162-1-2000x1333-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2162-1-2000x1333-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>为了兼顾不同群体的需求，让无论是在公园内玩耍的小孩还是路过休息的上班族，都拥有一个安全。舒适的空间，公厕采用了分散式布局，在各个位置都保持宽阔的视野。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361864" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2258-1-2000x1333.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2258-1-2000x1333.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2258-1-2000x1333-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2258-1-2000x1333-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2258-1-2000x1333-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>弧形的屋顶将厕所的四个空间连接在一起，既能促进空气流通和自然采光，让整个环境显得明亮清洁，同时也呈现出类似游乐场设施的外观，更契合「章鱼公园」的风格。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361865" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2273-1-2000x1333.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2273-1-2000x1333.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2273-1-2000x1333-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2273-1-2000x1333-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A2273-1-2000x1333-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>槇文彦希望希望这个公厕不仅仅是一个卫生间，还能为前来公园的民众提供一个休息的公共空间。</p>
<p><strong>最「原始」的公厕</strong></p>
<p>而设计师片山正通则希望公厕不那么像建筑，而是可以像树木和长凳一样与公园融为一体。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361867" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1210-1-2000x1334.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1334" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1210-1-2000x1334.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1210-1-2000x1334-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1210-1-2000x1334-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A1210-1-2000x1334-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>他的设计灵感来源于日本新石器时代的厕所 kawaya，又被成为「川屋」，顾名思义，即在河川边上建立的小屋，一般由硬化的土块或绑在一起的木头制成。</p>
<p>借鉴了「川屋」的概念，这座公厕将 15 面混凝土墙随机排列组合，间隔出宛若迷宫的三个独立空间，不同方向都有着出入口。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361868" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/metalocus_masamichi-katayama_wonderwall_toilet-kawaya_01.jpg" alt="" width="1467" height="1100" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/metalocus_masamichi-katayama_wonderwall_toilet-kawaya_01.jpg 1467w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/metalocus_masamichi-katayama_wonderwall_toilet-kawaya_01-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/metalocus_masamichi-katayama_wonderwall_toilet-kawaya_01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/metalocus_masamichi-katayama_wonderwall_toilet-kawaya_01-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1467px) 100vw, 1467px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361866" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A3232-1-2000x1333.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A3232-1-2000x1333.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A3232-1-2000x1333-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A3232-1-2000x1333-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/O0A3232-1-2000x1333-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>片山正通表示，这种设计让使用者与公厕进行更多交互，就像在游乐场玩游戏一样，但对于十分内急的人来说可能就有点崩溃了。</p>
<p>不过这样的厕所大概会是日本文豪谷崎润一郎的最爱，他曾在《<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/4151117/">阴翳礼赞</a>》以诗意的文字来描写那些与大自热融为一体的厕所。</p>
<blockquote><p>厕所极为适合于虫鸣、鸟声，也适合于月夜，是品味四季变化和万物情趣的最理想的去处。</p></blockquote>
<p>目前这五座公厕已经面向公众开放，而剩余的 12 座公厕，也会在明年陆续完成，以迎接 2021 年东京奥运会的到来。</p>
<p>值得一提的是，这些公厕里清洁工人的服装，是由潮流教父 NIGO 设计，日本财团会长笹川阳平认为这可以提升清洁工人工作的积极性。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361832" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/maintenance.jpg" alt="" width="2553" height="1481" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/maintenance.jpg 2553w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/maintenance-360x209.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/maintenance-768x446.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/maintenance-1024x594.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2553px) 100vw, 2553px" /></p>
<p>这些设计大师打造的公厕，颠覆了很多人对公厕的印象，原来公厕也是可以一个景点，一个艺术品。</p>
<p>如果你下一次到日本旅行，不妨到这些设计独特的公厕体验一番。</p>
<h3>世界上颜值最高的公厕，应该是怎样的</h3>
<p>除了「东京厕所」项目，世界各地也有着不少设计精美的公厕。</p>
<p><a href="http://www.designcurial.com/news/the-10-best-public-toilet-designs-of-2017-5971621/"><strong>建筑设计网站 DesignCurial</strong></a><strong> 每年都会对全球 1000 多个公厕进行评选，从设计、创新能力以及与周围环境的关系等维度，选出全球 TOP10 公厕，堪称是「公厕界的米其林指南」。</strong></p>
<p>在挪威斯泰格斯坦观景台上的山顶厕所在如厕的同时可以将挪威峡湾山谷的美景尽收眼底。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361871" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2b0848f26d571043e177e945db6d6524.jpg" alt="" width="1503" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2b0848f26d571043e177e945db6d6524.jpg 1503w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2b0848f26d571043e177e945db6d6524-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2b0848f26d571043e177e945db6d6524-768x511.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2b0848f26d571043e177e945db6d6524-1024x681.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1503px) 100vw, 1503px" /></p>
<p>新西兰惠灵顿 Kumutoto 公厕，已经成为一个地标，夸张的造型让你很难在街头忽略它。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1361873" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/KT4_Studio_Pacific.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1409" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/KT4_Studio_Pacific.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/KT4_Studio_Pacific-360x254.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/KT4_Studio_Pacific-768x541.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/KT4_Studio_Pacific-1024x721.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>澳大利亚街头的自动弹起式公厕 UriLift，你以为它是路上的一个井盖，可在晚上高峰期时它会自动升起变成一个公厕。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361874 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-07-15-49.2020-08-30-07_16_48.gif" alt="" width="534" height="530" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-07-15-49.2020-08-30-07_16_48.gif 534w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020-08-30-07-15-49.2020-08-30-07_16_48-360x357.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px" /></p>
<p>而南京牛首山景区内的八个公厕，也曾入选 DesignCurial 的全球 Top 10 公厕榜单。厕所廊道本身就是观景台，透过 U 型窗能看到景区内各个景点。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361878 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2-c39d45b8f16fdd9fce7c36a12e9215d5_720w.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2-c39d45b8f16fdd9fce7c36a12e9215d5_720w.jpg 720w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2-c39d45b8f16fdd9fce7c36a12e9215d5_720w-360x360.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></p>
<p><a href="https://k.sina.cn/article_5135808743_1321e38e701900jeu4.html">建筑师李竹表示</a>，希望景区里的厕所，除了解决人们基本「三急」需求之外，也是旅游时候人们邂逅的一个地方，希望能跟风景一样，成为人们享受美的窗口，这就要靠设计来解决。</p>
<h3>公厕的意义，不再只是为了方便</h3>
<p>1932 年，暨南大学教授周谷城在《东方杂志》上写下了他的「新年梦想」：</p>
<blockquote><p>我梦想中的未来中国首要之条件便是：人人有机会坐在抽水马桶上大便。</p></blockquote>
<p>尽管中国对于公厕的文字记载最早出现在《周礼》，但直到 1864 年，在上海租界才建起了全中国第一座现代意义的公共厕所。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361875 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/qkimagesbjdabjda201904bjda20190413-1-l.jpg" alt="" width="677" height="359" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/qkimagesbjdabjda201904bjda20190413-1-l.jpg 677w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/qkimagesbjdabjda201904bjda20190413-1-l-360x191.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 677px) 100vw, 677px" /></p>
<p>清末民国时期，就连都城北京也缺乏完善的公共厕所，民众对于随地大小便习以为常。当时在北京教会医院工作的苏格兰人<a href="https://www.huxiu.com/article/286421.html">德贞（John H. Dudgeon）直言北京街头就是一个巨大的公厕</a>：</p>
<blockquote><p>北京的街道基本上就是公厕，每天都堆积着大量的人和动物的粪便。中国男人习惯天黑后就蹲在街上大解，甚至大白天在最繁忙的街道上也有人这么做。巷口及倒塌或无人居住的房屋，经常也被变为一个另类的便溺场所。</p></blockquote>
<p><strong>以至于在八国联军入侵北京后，不得不下达「禁止民众随地大小便」的命令，并在北京建起了第一座公厕。</strong></p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361876 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v.jpg" alt="" width="578" height="412" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v.jpg 578w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v-360x257.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 578px) 100vw, 578px" /></p>
<p>时至今日，中国的公厕已经基本普及，我们不必再羡慕欧美等发达国家。不过新时代对于公厕的要求也不仅仅是让人方便，还需要与城市和社区文化更紧密结合。</p>
<p>清华大学美术学院协同创新生态设计中心的厕所研究与设计项目组，曾提出了<a href="http://www.artdesign.org.cn/article/view/id/34193">厕所设计的基本原则（HEBC</a>）：</p>
<ul>
<li>人本设计（Humanistic design）</li>
<li>生态优先（Ecological priority）</li>
<li>商业可持续（Businesssustainability）</li>
<li>文化塑造（Culture shaping）</li>
</ul>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1361877 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/SQEWkXABgx9BqZZI-y87.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="694" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/SQEWkXABgx9BqZZI-y87.jpg 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/SQEWkXABgx9BqZZI-y87-360x390.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p><strong>他们希望借助「设计思维」，将健康、卫生、环保的设计理念与公厕结合，改变大众对于公厕的认知，构建一种新型的厕所文化。</strong></p>
<p>不过高颜值的网红公厕未必就是好的公共厕所，<strong>只有将设计感和功能性相结合，给使用者带来贴心体验、给城市增添美感，才是真正的「最美公厕」，而设计始终会是其中重要的驱动力。</strong></p>
<p>题图及部分配图来自：The Tokyo Toilet</p>